        <div class="epiphany-bridge" id="p2-epiphany">\
          <p class="epiphany-line" id="p2-ep-1">I used to think the people who posted every day were just more confident than me.</p>\
          <p class="epiphany-line" id="p2-ep-2">Turns out they weren't. They just had something to say before they hit record.</p>\
