        <h2 class="plan-title"><span class="name-accent" id="p2-display-name">Your</span> Video 1: I'm Doing This</h2>\
\
        <div class="script-box">\
          <div class="script-header">\
            <p class="script-label">Your Video 1 Script</p>\
            <button class="copy-btn" id="p2-copy-btn">Copy Script</button>\
          </div>\
          <p class="script-line" id="p2-script-line-1">Hey, I'm <span id="p2-script-name"></span>. And I'm doing something that honestly scares me a little bit.</p>\
          <p class="script-line" id="p2-script-line-2">I've been thinking about posting for a while now, and I kept telling myself I'd wait until I felt more ready, until I had better equipment, until I knew exactly what I was doing. But at some point you have to stop planning and just start, and that's what this is. This is me starting. I don't have it all figured out, and I'm not going to pretend that I do, but I have something real to say and I think that matters more than having the perfect setup or the perfect script or the perfect anything.</p>\
        </div>\
\
        <div class="result-cta">\
          <a href="https://content.coloradomastermind.com/yes" class="btn-cta" id="p2-goto-v2">I'M READY FOR VIDEO 2</a>\
          <p class="cta-note">Instant access &middot; All 7 scripts unlocked immediately</p>\
        </div>\
\
        <div class="social-proof">\
          <span>Join <strong>300+</strong> creators who turned their Video 1 script into all seven.</span>\
